{"title":"Paper. ERGE-2025-1","guid":"","filepath":"/Users/criaah/Vault/📚 Resources/Mapas-Mentales/Entidades clínicas/Gastroenterología/Paper. ERGE-2025-1.smmx","root":{"id":"0","parent":"-1","text":"Manejo de la Enfermedad por Reflujo\\NGastroesofágico (ERGE) - Recomendaciones LATAM\\N(**2025**, **Expertos Latinoamericanos**)","guid":"cH6MfzTlsZiMgLS2plJcYg","children":[{"id":"1","parent":"0","text":"› Definición ★","guid":"","children":[{"id":"2","parent":"1","text":"◊ Síntomas o lesiones por retorno del contenido gástrico al esófago que incomodan y alteran calidad de vida","guid":"chNisbJlYfS6h5ArrBk6tA","children":[]},{"id":"3","parent":"1","text":"◊ Prevalencia: 1 de cada 5 adultos","guid":"bArXHNkQKPV_fYByoKEgqA","children":[]},{"id":"4","parent":"1","text":"◊ Definición de **Montreal** (**N. Vakil et al., 2006**)","guid":"5P5qt7ftQdrCQ1u7DdcD2g","children":[]}]},{"id":"5","parent":"0","text":"› Fisiopatología\\N(Multifactorial) ★","guid":"","children":[{"id":"6","parent":"5","text":"◊ Pérdida barrera\\Nantirreflujo","guid":"rNIszNLJ91JV74AsKCRKmQ","children":[{"id":"7","parent":"6","text":"• Relajaciones transitorias e incompetencia del esfínter esofágico inferior (EEI)","guid":"MTzzwu2rbrmMwYUpvrFDQQ","children":[]},{"id":"8","parent":"6","text":"• Hernia hiatal (HH)","guid":"dznhIkRT1cTXx22earsOIQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"9","parent":"5","text":"◊ Motilidad esofágica anormal","guid":"uxQl6G4R7fdlZGmZsQ31wg","children":[]},{"id":"10","parent":"5","text":"◊ Secreción salival disminuida","guid":"x01-_vi9AUWCj9mvTmZu1g","children":[]},{"id":"11","parent":"5","text":"◊ Pobre resistencia epitelio esofágico","guid":"wvcCn0jGxlg2AlgOUTiZGg","children":[]},{"id":"12","parent":"5","text":"◊ Vaciamiento gástrico retrasado","guid":"ztgZaxmAbcUl7ZcYvmV3gA","children":[]},{"id":"13","parent":"5","text":"◊ Reflujo duodenogastroesofágico","guid":"ExxKbvGj0daYkAnXtxs1cg","children":[]},{"id":"14","parent":"5","text":"◊ Rol de la Obesidad","guid":"X4R-srUo29yGvlnwSmuu2Q","children":[{"id":"15","parent":"14","text":"• Alteraciones anatomía y fisiología unión gastroesofágica (UEG)","guid":"Sj5V2Eycs8fV6ArakZcVIw","children":[]},{"id":"16","parent":"14","text":"• Grasa visceral asociada a esofagitis por reflujo (**Matsuzaki J et al., 2015**)","guid":"0Xu2KUb6nW7MlqphgfHGxw","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"17","parent":"0","text":"› Síntomas\\N(Basado en\\NTabla 1)","guid":"Jx0LvKpYOd-yl-MJipI8LQ","children":[{"id":"18","parent":"17","text":"◊ Típicos ★","guid":"tgmPxyovm5kjeEIVELc4ww","children":[{"id":"19","parent":"18","text":"• Pirosis (quemadura retroesternal ascendente)","guid":"MmCcoGVELT6DNRPd0EpSPA","children":[]},{"id":"20","parent":"18","text":"• Regurgitación (retorno sin esfuerzo contenido gástrico)","guid":"qe_ztugWdha4A_kW_gjbNg","children":[]},{"id":"21","parent":"18","text":"• Frecuencia: Leves (≥ 2 días/sem), Mod-Graves (≥ 1 vez/sem)","guid":"dz61PrIDK_7bmJInsoU5QA","children":[]},{"id":"22","parent":"18","text":"• Ocurrencia: Postprandial, Nocturna (altera sueño/calidad vida)","guid":"hJzcEc0CQ5iy90A8OVws6w","children":[]},{"id":"23","parent":"18","text":"• Sensibilidad (30-76%), Especificidad (62-92%) → Diagnóstico presuntivo, requieren pruebas objetivas","guid":"aoU6nAkJ-OQNn8cTm96KUg","children":[]}]},{"id":"24","parent":"17","text":"◊ Atípicos","guid":"R1P0bLGpQO3A5JrtF_hDVg","children":[{"id":"25","parent":"24","text":"• Dolor torácico (Indistinguible de cardiopatía isquémica → requiere descarte cardiovascular)","guid":"sy8JpQ9npRR-f1HfKO05iA","children":[]}]},{"id":"26","parent":"17","text":"◊ Otros (No\\Ncaracterísticos)","guid":"dflVWHDCZvi-z6c8GY8dtg","children":[{"id":"27","parent":"26","text":"• Sialorrea, Eructos, Hipo","guid":"7JLdvemZsEksEUkiN2zJVw","children":[]},{"id":"28","parent":"26","text":"• Disfagia (★ Signo de alarma → evaluación precisa)","guid":"u9W37gW3SdJnG0IwuLB6nQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"29","parent":"17","text":"◊ Extraesofágicos\\N(MEE) ★","guid":"HTYjdM74NfqmbUExddsggg","children":[{"id":"30","parent":"29","text":"• Asociación establecida: Tos, Laringitis, Asma bronquial, Erosiones dentales","guid":"50WszSMPU1bNh8XMuzuCeQ","children":[]},{"id":"31","parent":"29","text":"• Posible asociación: Otitis media, Sinusitis, Fibrosis pulmonar","guid":"cbgU02LNBxmsgqOqNBttxQ","children":[]},{"id":"32","parent":"29","text":"• Requieren pruebas objetivas para atribuirse a ERGE","guid":"os-exUPb2wpPGF6qYGshKA","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"33","parent":"0","text":"› Complicaciones\\N(Basado en Tabla 1) ★","guid":"","children":[{"id":"34","parent":"33","text":"◊ Esofagitis erosiva (EE) (Más común, ~30% pacientes)","guid":"GRwO9zdkoolxLfNqggor4w","children":[]},{"id":"35","parent":"33","text":"◊ Estenosis esofágica","guid":"7FR9qiNlH3flgSdc0Q1ndw","children":[]},{"id":"36","parent":"33","text":"◊ Úlceras esofágicas","guid":"o2TjGmDR0SMe7BIpOG2jxw","children":[]},{"id":"37","parent":"33","text":"◊ Hemorragia digestiva (Hematemesis, Melena → ★ Datos de alarma)","guid":"wvIi-J7sl7PHp4jC5haBrQ","children":[]},{"id":"38","parent":"33","text":"◊ Esófago de Barrett (EB) (Más grave, 1-5% pacientes ERGE en endoscopia)","guid":"f1O8agGFHWC2JTuEHzgKtA","children":[{"id":"39","parent":"38","text":"• Riesgo Carcinogénico → Adenocarcinoma esofágico (ACE)","guid":"1bgyzfLRANXP70jH5-glDA","children":[]}]},{"id":"40","parent":"33","text":"◊ Adenocarcinoma de esófago (ACE)","guid":"JMfavyIhZ_7KbJNGEnHyCw","children":[]}]},{"id":"41","parent":"0","text":"◊ Factores de Riesgo\\Npara Complicaciones","guid":"","children":[{"id":"42","parent":"41","text":"• Sexo masculino","guid":"CuSLwsRdLx1875d06EBBrg","children":[]},{"id":"43","parent":"41","text":"• Edad > 50 años","guid":"R0Ov_p9yVPtv3hhemxGcUQ","children":[]},{"id":"44","parent":"41","text":"• Obesidad (especialmente central)","guid":"MB6L-wp8KKgqSzmu5AIdqg","children":[]},{"id":"45","parent":"41","text":"• Consumo de tabaco","guid":"UGatv7CI4KTjUrh6k2D-AA","children":[]},{"id":"46","parent":"41","text":"• Síntomas > 5 años duración","guid":"7yV2AJKVWVFDOFbNy4t8ww","children":[]},{"id":"47","parent":"41","text":"• Consumo de alcohol (Asociado a gravedad EE y presencia EB en hombres, **Matsuzaki J et al., 2015**)","guid":"bLTmzAXwi5VrBlk9S0mhkQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"48","parent":"0","text":"◊ ★ Datos de Alarma\\N(Sospechar complicaciones)","guid":"","children":[{"id":"49","parent":"48","text":"• Disfagia","guid":"DkJE5pRQW4hLtKxS-ocRug","children":[]},{"id":"50","parent":"48","text":"• Pérdida de peso","guid":"oOVa8w2emPBX9S0EQIXzCQ","children":[]},{"id":"51","parent":"48","text":"• Hemorragia digestiva (Hematemesis, Melena)","guid":"JmI4mGwU1zkj2zQ2oLCSdA","children":[]}]},{"id":"52","parent":"0","text":"- Diagnóstico\\N(Uso Racional\\Nde Pruebas)","guid":"Is0T5OXTOEgqBw4GuTH1NA","children":[{"id":"53","parent":"52","text":"› Prueba Terapéutica con IBP\\N(Inhibidores Bomba Protones) ★\\N(Rec. 3)","guid":"RtQ97EUuDyQCH73DGmtPaw","children":[{"id":"54","parent":"53","text":"◊ Indicación: Síntomas típicos sin datos de alarma","guid":"rxl2FrEune50pd6XpWwEYA","children":[]},{"id":"55","parent":"53","text":"◊ Duración: 2-4 sem (síntomas típicos), 4-8 sem (dolor torácico no cardiaco)","guid":"n6VzUuNpmO7OsRA0c7ISXQ","children":[]},{"id":"56","parent":"53","text":"◊ Dosis: Estándar (ver Tabla 2), 30-60 min antes desayuno","guid":"vMCm5PTv93s3Hg1ONwOCxg","children":[]},{"id":"57","parent":"53","text":"◊ Respuesta Positiva: Mejoría sintomática > 50%","guid":"VNXjFD24n4rrWeJU4a3XWg","children":[]},{"id":"58","parent":"53","text":"◊ Rendimiento: Sensibilidad (71-79%), Especificidad (~45%)","guid":"IqaL8hO6VITM_NUD3jjLUQ","children":[]},{"id":"59","parent":"53","text":"◊ No evidencia para prueba con P-CAB (Bloqueadores Ácido Competitivos Potasio)","guid":"i734x-_XWMK9KP4QwU8eKQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"60","parent":"52","text":"› Indicaciones Pruebas\\NDiagnósticas Confirmatorias ★\\N(Rec. 4)","guid":"3b5IW9stK20oefDVyyhGUw","children":[{"id":"61","parent":"60","text":"◊ Falla tratamiento IBP / P-CAB","guid":"XanACGp2acALQOYXkWADug","children":[]},{"id":"62","parent":"60","text":"◊ Manifestaciones extraesofágicas (MEE)\\N(especialmente sin síntomas típicos)","guid":"hscB_7vtjYW8gpJMNbSyZg","children":[]},{"id":"63","parent":"60","text":"◊ Candidatos a cirugía antirreflujo","guid":"juuIQlwRQKX4FuQq3_sgIw","children":[]},{"id":"64","parent":"60","text":"◊ Síntomas como tos, eructo excesivo, sospecha rumiación","guid":"qA_YTrRWDjfzgHBtReZVEA","children":[]},{"id":"65","parent":"60","text":"◊ Necesidad diagnóstico definitivo (descartar Trastornos Interacción\\NCerebro Intestino (TICI) si no hay evidencia ERGE post-prueba)","guid":"yo_4zwiu4f-tJx3rqCwHpQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"66","parent":"52","text":"› Endoscopia ★\\N(Rec. 5)","guid":"zR63H_FFCUQdAQQt__P8UA","children":[{"id":"67","parent":"66","text":"◊ Indicaciones:","guid":"uyebHjQVpc9JTq764kWWGA","children":[{"id":"68","parent":"67","text":"• Síntomas ERGE + Datos alarma","guid":"Oh10KPS9clWUL1d3G9Bprg","children":[]},{"id":"69","parent":"67","text":"• Riesgo Esófago de Barrett (EB)","guid":"cLIPXKX9d9tD054TsUc4lg","children":[]},{"id":"70","parent":"67","text":"• No respuesta a IBP / P-CAB","guid":"4nR_2T-Z-hA5Mgy46WCYIA","children":[]},{"id":"71","parent":"67","text":"• Recurrencia síntomas al suspender terapia","guid":"AYjxecSz3I6kjui-tnUKKA","children":[]},{"id":"72","parent":"67","text":"• Países alta incidencia Ca Gástrico + Signos alarma (baja\\Npeso, anemia, >45 años, melena, hist. familiar Ca gástrico)","guid":"Um186w5PrIzz4d3zw8GQZg","children":[]}]},{"id":"73","parent":"66","text":"◊ Hallazgos Concluyentes ERGE\\N(**Consenso Lyon 2.0**)","guid":"Yc-BLQs-tv18aKJmd72rew","children":[{"id":"74","parent":"73","text":"• Esofagitis (EE) Grado B, C, D (Clasificación Los Angeles)","guid":"hccyhMXZI_ND3Nj33PNqiA","children":[]},{"id":"75","parent":"73","text":"• Esófago de Barrett (EB) (comprobado por biopsias)","guid":"kQWxbmSmNr2N6T0moLUVMA","children":[]},{"id":"76","parent":"73","text":"• Estenosis péptica","guid":"Cv293RH7NTSl-z-CIsvclw","children":[]},{"id":"77","parent":"73","text":"• Esofagitis Grado A (NO evidencia definitiva)","guid":"yosp281Fi9KcpicyfTMSmA","children":[]}]},{"id":"78","parent":"66","text":"◊ Timing Óptimo: Realizar 2-4 semanas *después* de\\Nsuspender antisecretores (en ERGE no probada)","guid":"fl9uWefjmt2P-j6wqOGmyQ","children":[]},{"id":"79","parent":"66","text":"◊ EE Grave (Grado C/D): Repetir endoscopia post 8 sem IBP doble dosis\\N(evaluar cicatrización, descartar EB oculto)","guid":"AS3j7HrV7mmUebzXQi8B6g","children":[]},{"id":"80","parent":"66","text":"◊ Evaluación\\NCompleta:","guid":"Qw0go3AR3JSVpX7z8sZDmQ","children":[{"id":"81","parent":"80","text":"• Evaluar EE (Clasificación Los Angeles)","guid":"M-VtmTKPKBYe9f2RSa6Zbw","children":[]},{"id":"82","parent":"80","text":"• Describir hiato diafragmático (Clasificación Hill - retrovisión)","guid":"f7sx8fDJLYyBR1_KvIEJOg","children":[]},{"id":"83","parent":"80","text":"• Grados I, II: Normales","guid":"LEhRELHp768z6A4aNn_zxQ","children":[]},{"id":"84","parent":"80","text":"• Grados III, IV: Asociados a pobre respuesta IBP y EE","guid":"1cGK1zULxB4V_nMDwCZNNA","children":[]},{"id":"85","parent":"80","text":"• Medir longitud axial hernia hiatal (HH)","guid":"K972_iDpArMTHY9TSKGeGQ","children":[]},{"id":"86","parent":"80","text":"• Inspeccionar EB","guid":"PUek_9lkIi9OHuQWcHUwkw","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"87","parent":"52","text":"› Medición del Reflujo\\NGastroesofágico ★","guid":"F_cjtZDS2QhvIr3B6F4PmA","children":[{"id":"88","parent":"87","text":"◊ Indicación Principal (Rec. 6): Síntomas típicos sin\\Nrespuesta IBP/P-CAB, endoscopia normal (~70%)","guid":"KDuGwIPJp-4pGfK5t9H-AA","children":[{"id":"89","parent":"88","text":"• Obligatorio para diagnóstico ERGE","guid":"G0x4zxZUqVXpuGX_60CbRQ","children":[]},{"id":"90","parent":"88","text":"• Realizar *sin* tratamiento antisecretor","guid":"r-ALbETTWDh8O9dLCuEpNg","children":[]}]},{"id":"91","parent":"87","text":"◊ Métodos:","guid":"S7VQbjHO22b1Q58oav_LBg","children":[{"id":"92","parent":"91","text":"• pHmetría o\\NpH-Impedancia 24h\\N(Catéter)","guid":"3lBL_0CLtYzPi42njdqjbw","children":[{"id":"93","parent":"92","text":"• Colocación: 5 cm sobre EEI (por manometría)","guid":"UtaqnbNEMNI2U3MnKQtN7A","children":[]},{"id":"94","parent":"92","text":"• Disponibilidad: Frecuente en LATAM","guid":"tvJqmZ_bitJypgEsXkrkhQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"95","parent":"91","text":"• pHmetría con\\NCápsula Inalámbrica\\N(96h)","guid":"mgcDm25KrMF83gB8Sq05qA","children":[{"id":"96","parent":"95","text":"• Colocación: 6 cm sobre UEG (en endoscopia)","guid":"sns0vaUg_pWnVNplAT0gFg","children":[]},{"id":"97","parent":"95","text":"• Ventajas: >Tiempo, >Tolerancia, <Interferencia","guid":"Y06_2Z0hlOZ7MqgP-qj3Ug","children":[]},{"id":"98","parent":"95","text":"• Disponibilidad: Poca en LATAM (Arg, Bra, Ven)","guid":"e_qz5VTDQ28xGbaH4O8n2A","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"99","parent":"87","text":"◊ Métricas Diagnósticas\\N(**Consenso Lyon 2.0**)","guid":"2oXrhAQKDDyYXMt4oHngwg","children":[{"id":"100","parent":"99","text":"• Tiempo Exposición\\NÁcido (TEA) ★","guid":"_qfjZ7E10KuINJvQyQ2HnA","children":[{"id":"101","parent":"100","text":"• TEA > 6%: Diagnóstico positivo ERGE","guid":"Pr_2JUiR0mFeB0yvNt4JCw","children":[]},{"id":"102","parent":"100","text":"• TEA < 4%: Excluye ERGE","guid":"6D_BsoYytTHaXiuV5tKngw","children":[]},{"id":"103","parent":"100","text":"• TEA 4-6%: Indeterminado (~12%) → requiere métricas adicionales","guid":"w3qgkniV9bgw0oe-LPqjHA","children":[]},{"id":"104","parent":"100","text":"• Cápsula 96h: TEA ≥ 6% en ≥ 2 días (+), TEA < 4% en 4 días (-)","guid":"p6-0mKz2GC5MpowSgM9VBw","children":[]}]},{"id":"105","parent":"99","text":"• Asociación Sintomática\\N(IS, PSA) ★","guid":"DRtPM1U5Oh_JeVgQu7aHvQ","children":[{"id":"106","parent":"105","text":"• Con TEA normal,\\Nclasifica:","guid":"I8_hj2HGdEjQE45-qZ0m2w","children":[{"id":"107","parent":"106","text":"◊ Hipersensibilidad al Reflujo (TEA normal, AS +)","guid":"hkkyofkq92WH8n2qjXNHsw","children":[]},{"id":"108","parent":"106","text":"◊ Pirosis Funcional (TEA normal, AS -)","guid":"x1kHj_wNeHYDFVuGva2Y9Q","children":[]}]}]}]},{"id":"109","parent":"87","text":"◊ Indicaciones pH-Impedancia 24h\\N*SIN* Antisecretores (Rec. 7)","guid":"03sJdgvkTKOUq_EDaCkU-w","children":[{"id":"110","parent":"109","text":"• ERGE no probado + Eructos frecuentes (Discernir gástrico vs supragástrico)","guid":"HFUsT0jQLzMLP9dAN92o5w","children":[]},{"id":"111","parent":"109","text":"• Sospecha Rumiación (pH-Imp sospecha, Manometría+Imp postprandial confirma)","guid":"OWkUb34barhdqtRWAmZ6kA","children":[]},{"id":"112","parent":"109","text":"• Manifestaciones Extraesofágicas (MEE) (Tos, disfonía) (Detecta reflujo no ácido, #episodios, IBN, AS)","guid":"EuRvrUK9fyZXoyZzQ5vEig","children":[]}]},{"id":"113","parent":"87","text":"◊ Indicaciones pH-Impedancia 24h\\N*CON* Antisecretores (Rec. 8)","guid":"5vKTTRJlYC4DbO0TAUw9lg","children":[{"id":"114","parent":"113","text":"• ERGE probada + Síntomas persistentes con tto óptimo","guid":"ZH-Ut1PeJwrTcuxLuTvtnw","children":[]},{"id":"115","parent":"113","text":"• Única herramienta útil; detecta reflujo débil/no ácido","guid":"kK_sho5n9QqrXCMs-O6djQ","children":[]},{"id":"116","parent":"113","text":"• Discierne control inadecuado vs. sobreposición funcional","guid":"kjWkpB03chciBPCtf1F80w","children":[]}]},{"id":"117","parent":"87","text":"◊ Métricas Adicionales\\N(TEA 4-6%) (Rec. 9)","guid":"NXCfFfibCyTuOkJaqpNkhA","children":[{"id":"118","parent":"117","text":"• Impedancia Basal Nocturna (IBN) Media ★ (< 1500 Ω apoya ERGE, > 2500 Ω descarta)","guid":"yP40gQonijK7oTp6JPvhtQ","children":[]},{"id":"119","parent":"117","text":"• Número Episodios Reflujo ★ (> 80/24h apoya, < 40/24h descarta)","guid":"Rg_SA7w8ckQqe_zguB489A","children":[]},{"id":"120","parent":"117","text":"• Otros Apoyos: HH, EEI hipotensivo, alt. peristalsis, AS +","guid":"RcHFB13e55UdMVqWsP4E4Q","children":[]},{"id":"121","parent":"117","text":"• PSPW (Onda peristáltica post-reflujo): Descartada métrica útil","guid":"5qI1AIZtNdoLBfLuLIMRfg","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"122","parent":"52","text":"› Esofagograma y\\NVaciamiento Gástrico\\N(Rec. 10)","guid":"zh4Vj13GFrv0rwJduRtrOQ","children":[{"id":"123","parent":"122","text":"◊ Esofagograma: NO recomendado para diagnóstico ERGE\\N(Baja S/E, pobre correlación pH)","guid":"cruNOl0pLj2isnRggTh83g","children":[{"id":"124","parent":"123","text":"• Útil para anatomía, estenosis, esófago corto","guid":"YWZLR7xZabUIGzdm-KsMNw","children":[]}]},{"id":"125","parent":"122","text":"◊ Vaciamiento Gástrico: NO\\Nrecomendado para diagnóstico ERGE","guid":"hnN-YRHClppsiU0OJ8Mlnw","children":[{"id":"126","parent":"125","text":"• Puede estar retrasado, pero síntomas no predicen","guid":"HLYE0_41K7Scj3H46TJoWg","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"127","parent":"52","text":"› Manometría Esofágica Alta\\NResolución (MAR) ★ (Rec. 11)","guid":"R1X-CI3xkdMCeyCfE8UBxA","children":[{"id":"128","parent":"127","text":"◊ Prueba Complementaria (Apoya diagnóstico ERGE)","guid":"o2RMYn1fyVyffsGcJrt-9A","children":[]},{"id":"129","parent":"127","text":"◊ Indicaciones: Evaluación pre-quirúrgica antirreflujo, Falla post-fundoplicatura","guid":"4Gi7wACDgrUyap7wtxRHow","children":[]},{"id":"130","parent":"127","text":"◊ Hallazgos que apoyan ERGE: Morfología anormal UEG (Tipo III/HH), Barrera incompetente (↓presión/integral), Hipomotilidad (Chicago\\Nv4.0)","guid":"YvHrgcoZTvvzGRDaeRX2RA","children":[]},{"id":"131","parent":"127","text":"◊ Puntaje de Milán ★ (Probabilidad ERGE por MAR: <60 → 10% riesgo, >210 → 90% riesgo)","guid":"x_lg0v67xiqW6_DNS9rVZw","children":[]},{"id":"132","parent":"127","text":"◊ Maniobra Dinámica (Straight Leg Raise): ↑ Presión intraesofágica > 11 mmHg predice TEA > 6%","guid":"BWOJUOy6dCwXqyj4gkDk0A","children":[]},{"id":"133","parent":"127","text":"◊ Rol en Cirugía Antirreflujo (**Consenso Padua**): Excluir contraindicaciones motoras","guid":"e3mNDqn5lHHgHnMDYp2dSQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"134","parent":"52","text":"› Pruebas en Manifestaciones\\NExtraesofágicas (MEE) (Rec. 12)","guid":"lWAjgYOZZYjZngccDlzv-Q","children":[{"id":"135","parent":"134","text":"◊ Sin síntomas típicos: Investigar primero causas ≠ Reflujo (Amplio DDx)","guid":"lWuRD74nhAT0eCQPXxLWPg","children":[]},{"id":"136","parent":"134","text":"◊ Investigación ERGE: pH-Impedancia sin antisecretores (Elección)","guid":"ktNx4J7RdDNps31IEH5BEw","children":[]},{"id":"137","parent":"134","text":"◊ Pruebas NO recomendadas para ERGE en MEE: EGD, Laringoscopia, Esofagograma, pH faríngea, Pepsina salival","guid":"4pdsjMWRfo83JXwnvmbWoA","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"138","parent":"0","text":"- Tratamiento","guid":"","children":[{"id":"139","parent":"138","text":"› Modificaciones Estilo de\\NVida (MEV) ★ (Rec. 13)","guid":"sbmgqXwvjc0YirsCRO1oQQ","children":[{"id":"140","parent":"139","text":"◊ Para *todos*: Bajar peso (si aplica), Evitar fumar, Evitar alimentos desencadenantes (individualizar)","guid":"50XMrJdypgoRKlo7QeNgZA","children":[]},{"id":"141","parent":"139","text":"◊ Reflujo nocturno: Cenar temprano, Elevar cabecera cama (15-20cm), Dormir lado izquierdo","guid":"a0y3zGAIMcYnz1hUBl4z7w","children":[]}]},{"id":"142","parent":"138","text":"› ERGE No Erosiva\\N(ERNE) (Rec. 14)","guid":"exTN_UjLypeNM1TDl5us3w","children":[{"id":"143","parent":"142","text":"◊ Fármacos elección: IBP, P-CAB ★","guid":"_Hp2bhMLoXRrIQG4Bo2o4Q","children":[{"id":"144","parent":"143","text":"◊ Inicial: Dosis estándar x 4 semanas","guid":"mYyOfBFg2QfokYSM4jmgig","children":[]},{"id":"145","parent":"143","text":"◊ Mantenimiento: ★ Dosis mínima necesaria; Esquema intermitente o a demanda","guid":"7AhmoiBGsCALE68d4E4QbA","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"146","parent":"138","text":"› Terapia Adyuvante ★\\N(Rec. 15)","guid":"bs7HkxsF8bTks4JPEWV2ew","children":[{"id":"147","parent":"146","text":"◊ Síntomas ocasionales: Alginatos, Antiácidos, Protectores mucosa (Ej: Esoxx-One)","guid":"TYrQQFIvSolicZ7nXv3v3Q","children":[]},{"id":"148","parent":"146","text":"◊ Síntomas nocturnos no controlados con IBP: ARH2 (Antagonistas Receptores H2) por periodos cortos (2-4 sem)","guid":"iPACfUa0oVSOo8sU1eZhvQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"149","parent":"138","text":"› Otros Fármacos\\N(Rec. 16)","guid":"1dg5RrA5jFEvAThRLuiEnw","children":[{"id":"150","parent":"149","text":"◊ Procinéticos: SOLO si síntomas retraso vaciamiento gástrico","guid":"gB7_sF7ygA-b8n8S_6wHpA","children":[]},{"id":"151","parent":"149","text":"◊ Baclofeno (Agonista GABA-B): Si Regurgitación/Eructos predominan y no responden a IBP","guid":"IO4HAwjgrJN_gkEH3DEe8Q","children":[]}]},{"id":"152","parent":"138","text":"› ERGE Erosiva\\N(EE) (Rec. 17)","guid":"J4S9A5fC2fLyy2ZqDQjRtg","children":[{"id":"153","parent":"152","text":"◊ Inicial (8 semanas): ★","guid":"0SVwriLNEfAcj6QaxHlnHA","children":[{"id":"154","parent":"153","text":"• EE Leve (A, B): IBP o P-CAB dosis estándar","guid":"keiAp1HhTxPDh1no1RhCMg","children":[]},{"id":"155","parent":"153","text":"• EE Grave (C, D): IBP *doble* dosis o P-CAB dosis estándar","guid":"RjIFXxUD1gzch5KZGZOZyg","children":[]},{"id":"156","parent":"153","text":"• P-CAB > IBP en cicatrización (esp. graves)","guid":"hl45E6Ub4Xx9ZVEXob96eA","children":[]}]},{"id":"157","parent":"152","text":"◊ Mantenimiento: ★ IBP dosis estándar o P-CAB mitad dosis estándar","guid":"kunKD9GUT1AZr3IckhG8Qg","children":[{"id":"158","parent":"157","text":"• EE Grado A: Tto a demanda costo-efectivo","guid":"3Rep5LVERwBGBnmpBpc9uA","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"159","parent":"138","text":"› Esófago de Barrett\\N(EB) (Rec. 18)","guid":"o7CrX22oRzjt3HZl5QpmPw","children":[{"id":"160","parent":"159","text":"◊ Tratamiento: IBP continuo ★ (Control síntomas + Prevención progresión displasia/ACE)","guid":"UIGo6mOZRLDIY3CGkcRl4w","children":[{"id":"161","parent":"160","text":"• IBP ↓ riesgo ACE/DAG 71% (**Singh S et al., 2014**)","guid":"DKItzHFQ2j8Qnv-wW_lA3Q","children":[]}]},{"id":"162","parent":"159","text":"◊ Otros (Evidencia no suficiente): Estatinas, COX-2 inhib., Aspirina","guid":"CiK0tQ1q_TwCe19A1Ym9Yg","children":[]}]},{"id":"163","parent":"138","text":"› ERGE Refractaria y\\NSobreposición Funcional","guid":"srO86q8dhp-HtTy3gfFaiQ","children":[{"id":"164","parent":"163","text":"◊ Conceptos\\NClave ★","guid":"yRzCHRlMhGrmZEQ1Dhk_eA","children":[{"id":"165","parent":"164","text":"• Definición ERGE Refractaria: Evidencia objetiva ERGE pese a IBP doble dosis x 8 sem","guid":"j-Kr2M7mcPcRGN4PP8Hq9A","children":[]},{"id":"166","parent":"164","text":"• Causas falla aparente: Adherencia, adm. incorrecta, farmacogenética, dx incorrecto (EEo)","guid":"-i77v6WsDKLk6dxYaM2cqA","children":[]},{"id":"167","parent":"164","text":"• Predictores Rpta Tto (**Gyawali et al., 2021**): TEA >0.5% y >40 reflujos (con doble IBP) → Rpta Cirugía (79%)","guid":"VkeX18EZx5o4PXPRsl2IqA","children":[]}]},{"id":"168","parent":"163","text":"◊ Optimización Tto\\NMédico (Rec. 19) ★","guid":"M_rMD5YFNL5pI3XsWn1UtQ","children":[{"id":"169","parent":"168","text":"• Comprobar Adherencia/Dosificación","guid":"GTo6_GUwmgsjaPFdBWKHwQ","children":[]},{"id":"170","parent":"168","text":"• Usar Dosis Doble IBP / Dividir Dosis","guid":"Oop-tKE2kZ1CUR8QUWYzvA","children":[]},{"id":"171","parent":"168","text":"• Cambiar a otro IBP","guid":"ZUZNazx6qBIODx6WAEHqag","children":[]},{"id":"172","parent":"168","text":"• Optar por P-CAB","guid":"OEdmEZHKyLbncfnUfiHKPA","children":[]},{"id":"173","parent":"168","text":"• Usar Tto Adyuvantes (Alginatos, Protectores)","guid":"dwdgL2i66oXa3vbS_Iod3w","children":[]}]},{"id":"174","parent":"163","text":"◊ Manejo Sobreposición\\NFuncional (Rec. 20, 21) ★","guid":"ZA5b1-0u7SLWkJb9J82k6A","children":[{"id":"175","parent":"174","text":"• Investigar TICI (Dispepsia, SII) - frecuente","guid":"_7vBk2yW0MT7Hg3SuAFPDQ","children":[]},{"id":"176","parent":"174","text":"• Tto: Optimizar antisecretores + Neuromoduladores\\N(Tricíclicos, ISRS) + Terapias Psicológicas (Hipnoterapia, TCC)","guid":"VwgNWn_VsRGfgGZ6xobZSw","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"177","parent":"138","text":"› Tratamiento Manifestaciones\\NExtraesofágicas (MEE) (Rec. 22)","guid":"VyJrMUg-yV7v5TovW-YRrg","children":[{"id":"178","parent":"177","text":"◊ SOLO si evidencia objetiva ERGE","guid":"ShNwXq-FLqdsRQkl1B5tHA","children":[]},{"id":"179","parent":"177","text":"◊ Tratamiento: IBP DOBLE dosis x 12 semanas ★","guid":"ahbff7_xh1Sjwjpuews-dA","children":[]},{"id":"180","parent":"177","text":"◊ NO tto de prueba sin ERGE demostrado","guid":"r2UiM6CrMYIw7DQIhA_4QA","children":[]}]},{"id":"181","parent":"138","text":"› Tratamiento\\NEndoscópico ★","guid":"fWuFDDKbPSRJZU8upgg0hg","children":[{"id":"182","parent":"181","text":"◊ Fundoplicatura Transoral Sin Incisiones\\N(TIF - EsophyX 2.0) (Rec. 23)","guid":"ADcdnPbmxvI2lPJddfdR7w","children":[{"id":"183","parent":"182","text":"• Indicación: Selección estricta (HH < 2cm, Hill I/II, EE A/B)","guid":"BnerbDsD5hUS28BgnzK7zw","children":[]},{"id":"184","parent":"182","text":"• Eficacia demostrada vs Placebo/IBP (RESPECT, TEMPO trials)","guid":"UhVFz1Ak6NSv6SDjf811sQ","children":[]},{"id":"185","parent":"182","text":"• Procedimiento con > evidencia vs otros endoscópicos","guid":"757mKHH4Vx2NvjdxXN-9pQ","children":[]},{"id":"186","parent":"182","text":"• Experiencia incipiente LATAM","guid":"952fhf0TgHEg5wYV187BfA","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"187","parent":"138","text":"› Tratamiento Quirúrgico\\N(Cirugía Antirreflujo) ★\\N(Rec. 24)","guid":"3Av75F286tcytC_oAvjYcg","children":[{"id":"188","parent":"187","text":"◊ Indicaciones: ERGE certero, HH grande,\\NRegurgitación predom., Sin trastorno motor grave","guid":"FMOnFQrXEa24IRwzwd4aLQ","children":[]},{"id":"189","parent":"187","text":"◊ Elección: Fundoplicatura\\NLaparoscópica (FPL)","guid":"tTsTEt3qQ5kHy6c2j-YWEQ","children":[]},{"id":"190","parent":"187","text":"◊ Evaluación Pre-Op: Demostrar ERGE,\\NMAR (descartar contraindicaciones)","guid":"qPEENI1MQR18Jgi2DA6-mA","children":[]},{"id":"191","parent":"187","text":"◊ Eficacia: ≥ Tto médico; Superior en pirosis refractaria\\N(**Spechler SJ et al., 2019**)","guid":"6qtZ75hHKrBUadG2R-13wQ","children":[]},{"id":"192","parent":"187","text":"◊ Duración/Recurrencia: Variable (10-27%\\Nrecurrencia 3-5a, hasta 62% usan medicación a 10a)","guid":"lh2U2lIvUXHLngGGYpzipg","children":[]},{"id":"193","parent":"187","text":"◊ Tipos: Parcial (Toupet, Dor) vs Completa (Nissen) -\\NEficacia similar, Parcial < disfagia","guid":"2X198NeWlaqnC4X4AfxiTA","children":[]},{"id":"194","parent":"187","text":"◊ Conclusión: Eficaz, baja morbilidad, alta satisfacción en bien seleccionados","guid":"QRblQIVhB6TGd4UrcH9KbQ","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"195","parent":"0","text":"- ERGE en Condiciones\\NEspeciales","guid":"DQjzGeOAncRr02j-aa-Lkg","children":[{"id":"196","parent":"195","text":"› Esofagitis Eosinofílica\\N(EEo) (Rec. 25) ★","guid":"c67nHVVQT5vIcqcEy4INew","children":[{"id":"197","parent":"196","text":"◊ Sospecha: ERGE persistente + Disfagia + Atopia + Impactación","guid":"x4dcFFkgZ6PrGvWxE8nU9Q","children":[]},{"id":"198","parent":"196","text":"◊ Dx: Endoscopia + Biopsias prox/distal (> 15 eos/CAP)","guid":"Slq5TcbCqZCsFIkoaWHQNA","children":[]}]},{"id":"199","parent":"195","text":"› Embarazo (Rec. 26) ★","guid":"TOPMWoYcal-ijzcwHKIV_Q","children":[{"id":"200","parent":"199","text":"◊ Frecuente (~2/3), empeora tarde, resuelve postparto","guid":"KDSZ9h1BNljH07XpPajJPw","children":[]},{"id":"201","parent":"199","text":"◊ Dx: Clínico","guid":"cu0OYjploXwImp1toiFEHQ","children":[]},{"id":"202","parent":"199","text":"◊ Tto: 1° MEV; Leve: Antiácidos/Sucralfato; Grave: ARH2/IBP (Omeprazol Cat C, resto Cat B)","guid":"DbtmuYQw4peFg8BGdSI0PQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"203","parent":"195","text":"› Adulto Mayor (Rec. 27 -\\Nnumeración del doc: 26) ★","guid":"ytQ0D5OcMezL4Q4D6bZ1tA","children":[{"id":"204","parent":"203","text":"◊ Más frecuente/grave, síntomas atípicos/leves","guid":"wz9ZD_ldDUcuzrf0oIPxmQ","children":[]},{"id":"205","parent":"203","text":"◊ Dx: Endoscopia recomendada","guid":"ggp-eQSp_FhudyRINqfhfw","children":[]},{"id":"206","parent":"203","text":"◊ Tto: IBP/P-CAB (principios = jóvenes)","guid":"sjyNAI1DZN6NuRRLuj2Qzw","children":[]}]},{"id":"207","parent":"195","text":"› Obesidad (Rec. 28 -\\Nnumeración del doc: 27) ★","guid":"rsHXljWPFi2VIisdF4nGBg","children":[{"id":"208","parent":"207","text":"◊ Factor riesgo ERGE (↑ Presión intraabd.)","guid":"lM9EusV5YfRVlDXirWgN7g","children":[]},{"id":"209","parent":"207","text":"◊ Cx Bariátrica con ERGE objetiva → Elección: Derivación Gastroyeyunal Y-Roux (DGYR)","guid":"LqFA3hSPOjhY1T5zFoWt9Q","children":[]}]},{"id":"210","parent":"195","text":"› Infección por Helicobacter pylori (H. pylori)\\N(Rec. 29 - numeración del doc: 28) ★","guid":"IB1Fuih5ieIgGZPpbeG8Vw","children":[{"id":"211","parent":"210","text":"◊ NO causal de ERGE","guid":"kMYd6pr41v3F_sp81XVMaQ","children":[]},{"id":"212","parent":"210","text":"◊ Erradicación: NO aumenta riesgo ACE (**Wiklund A-K et al., 2024**), NO contraindicada,\\NNO exacerba ERGE, RECOMENDADA si tto IBP prolongado","guid":"Ku7O5ur9yOC76DM8f8jueA","children":[]}]},{"id":"213","parent":"195","text":"› Análogos de GLP-1 (Agonistas) (Rec.\\N30, 31 - numeración del doc: 29, 30) ★","guid":"vRDaIjJflAzKhyNr3wwuLw","children":[{"id":"214","parent":"213","text":"◊ Uso en ERGE (Rec. 30): NO contraindicado;\\NPUEDE empeorar síntomas (↓ vaciamiento gástrico)","guid":"YC5j7J9Eb4RF_DbYhFTY-Q","children":[]},{"id":"215","parent":"213","text":"◊ Pre-Endoscopia (Rec. 31): Individualizar riesgo broncoaspiración;\\NSuspender 1 sem antes si síntomas retención gástrica (Recomendación AGA)","guid":"EjJIlTkmatnoH9-Id_VmAw","children":[]}]}]}]},"node_count":215,"relations":[],"cross_references":[],"specialty":"Gastroenterología","folder":"Entidades clínicas/Gastroenterología","filename":"Paper. ERGE-2025-1","id":"map_672","resolved_references":[]}